{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_01_03",
  "title": "白石千紗 3話 お揃いのシュシュ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（サニーピースのライブが間近に迫ってきたある日）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The Sunny Peace live is drawing near.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　千紗、何してるんだ？\nわざわざリビングで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey. Chisa‚ what are you doing\nhere in the living room?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.833333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、お、お疲れさまです……\nちょっと、こんなのを作ってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ h-hello.\nI’m just… making a little something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.733333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それ……シュシュか\n自分で使う用？　それとも、誰かにあげるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are those… scrunchies?\nAre they for you? Or for someone else?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "はい、えっと……サニピのみんなに、です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Someone else‚ um… the members of Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "衣装とは別に、何かお揃いのものが\nあってもいいかなって思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought we could wear matching accessories\nbesides just our costumes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "シュシュなら簡単に作れますし\nいろいろ使い道もあるから、邪魔になりませんし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Scrunchies are nice and easy to make‚\ncan be used for all sorts of things‚ and don’t get in the way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "実は、みんなのパーソナルカラーも\nしっかり取り入れてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m working in the personal colors\nfor each member as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんはオレンジで、怜ちゃんはブルー……\nそんな感じで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Orange for Sakura-chan‚ blue for Rei-chan.\nLike this‚ see?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "……私って、いつもみんなに支えられてばっかりで\nまだまだダメダメだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Everyone has been giving me so much support.\nI still have a long way to go‚ I know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "せめてこういう、私なりのやり方で\nみんなを支えてあげたいって思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I want to do whatever I can\nto support them‚ in my own way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……必要な手伝いとか材料があったら\n遠慮なく言ってくれていいからな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Don't hesitate to ask me\nif you need help with materials or anything else.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、本当ですか？\nそれじゃあ、あの……一個だけ、いいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-really?\nIn that case… there is one thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "小さいのでいいので……\n新しいミシンが、欲しいなぁ……なんて……えへへ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just a small one would be fine…\nBut I’d like… a new sewing machine? Hehe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 85.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（そしてライブ当日がやって来た。本番直前）\n（千紗達サニーピースは円陣を組んで、気合充分だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The day of the live arrives. Right before taking to the stage‚)\n(Chisa and the rest of Sunny Peace form a circle‚ pumped up and ready to go.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "ふう…………っ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.03333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 94.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 95.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫か、千紗\nリラックスして楽しんでくればいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you okay‚ Chisa?\nRelax and enjoy it. You’ll be fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 99.83333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "はい……ありがとうございます\nでも、実は緊張は……そこまでじゃないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… Thank you.\nBut‚ to be honest… I’m not that nervous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "不思議なんですけど……\nお揃いのシュシュを着けてると、怖くないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a strange feeling.\nWearing these matching scrunchies is really soothing my nerves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 113.73333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "お揃いのシュシュ、か……\nそういえば、みんなも凄く喜んでくれてたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Matching scrunchies‚ huh?\nThe girls did all really like them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 120.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ。ちょっと、安心しました\nライブ前に渡せたので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. I’m glad I was able to give it to them\nbefore the live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "これで今日のライブも……\nいつも以上に、一緒になって頑張れると思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now the live is actually here…\nI know I can do my very best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 131.26666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、胸を張って…………ん？\n千紗、あそこにシュシュが一つ、余ってないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ go knock ‘em dead… hm?\nChisa‚ is that a spare scrunchie over there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 139.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "え？　……ああ、あれは違います\nみんなの分はちゃんと渡してありますから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Oh‚ no‚ that’s something else.\nI’ve given all the girls the ones for them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3266.6666666669926,
          "startTime": 146.066666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 146.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（舞台袖のテーブルに置きっぱなしのシュシュ）\n（千紗はそれを一度取りに行き、戻ってくる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Chisa goes over to a table at the wings of the stage.)\n(She picks up a scrunchie and then comes back over.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 152.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、これは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ this one is special.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 152.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_01_03-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんのぶん……です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s for you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
