      "text": "俺もサニピの一員として着けてほしい……ってことか\nありがとう。ここから精一杯応援するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So… you want me to wear this as a member of Sunny Peace.\nThank you. I’ll be supporting you from here.",
        "id": ""
